{"article_id":"TIsdW5Ivp9YlJSdf","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The woman","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"who accuses US Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh of sexual assault","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"has been given extra time","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"to decide","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"whether she will testify against him at a confirmation hearing .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Allegations from a university professor , Christine Blasey Ford , emerged in the US media last week .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"She gave details of an incident","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"which she says","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"happened at a party in 1982 .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"Her lawyer has accused Republicans of trying to `` bully '' her with `` arbitrary '' and `` aggressive '' deadlines .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"The Friday deadline","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"given by the Senate judiciary committee","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"is now reported to have been switched to later on Saturday .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"President Donald Trump attacked Prof Ford 's credibility on Friday ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"if the attack had been `` as bad","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"as she says '' ,","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"she would have reported it to the authorities sooner .","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"Prof Ford insists","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"she is ready to testify at the hearing ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"but negotiations over certain conditions","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"she has set out ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"including it not taking place until next Thursday ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"have delayed proceedings .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"The committee originally granted her a deadline of 22:00 on Friday","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"( 02:00 GMT Saturday )","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"to agree to revised terms","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"- though it is not yet known what these are .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"But the professor 's lawyer , Debra Katz , demanded another day","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"to decide ,","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"saying :","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"`` Its sole purpose is to bully Dr Ford","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"and deprive her of the ability","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"to make a considered decision","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"that has life-altering implications for her and her family . ''","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"In response , Senator Chuck Grassley","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"- the lead Republican on the committee -","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"said","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"he had granted Prof Ford `` another extension ''","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"- which ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"according to the New York Times ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"runs until 14:30 on Saturday","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"( 18:30 GMT ) .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"The allegation against Judge Kavanaugh , President Donald Trump 's pick for the US top court , became public last week .","depth":4},{"id":44,"text":"It emerged Prof Ford had detailed the alleged assault in a confidential letter to the top Democratic senator on the judiciary committee , Dianne Feinstein , in July .","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"As the judge neared confirmation ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"news about the letter leaked to US media .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"Ms Feinstein then confirmed","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"she had passed it onto the FBI .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"After days of continued media speculation , Prof Ford went on record in a Washington Post article as the mystery accuser ,","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"detailing the alleged assault .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"She said","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Mr Kavanaugh tried to drunkenly remove her clothing at a party ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"pinned her to a bed","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"and covered her mouth","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"when she was 15","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"and he was 17 .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"Since then , her lawyers have been in a back-and-forth with the judicial committee ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"trying to agree on terms for her to testify .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"She had asked for a number of preconditions ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"including not testifying with Mr Kavanaugh in the room and the subpoenaing of his friend , Mark Judge ,","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"who","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"she said","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"witnessed the alleged attempted rape .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Some Republicans ,","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"including President Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"have accused her and Democratic politicians of deliberately trying to delay and obstruct the judge 's confirmation ,","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"and urged them to push forward .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"The feelings are strong on both sides","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"- with both Prof Ford and Brett Kavanaugh and his wife both receiving threats and rallies of support over the matter .","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"The choice of a new justice for the Supreme Court is pivotal ,","depth":4},{"id":71,"text":"as it often gives the final word on highly contentious laws","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"and its nine judges have an immense impact on US public life .","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"As Mr Trump 's pick , Brett Kavanaugh has to first be approved by the Senate","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"before he can take his seat","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"- but","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"before that vote can happen ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"he has to be approved by the judiciary committee ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"where Prof Ford may testify .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"The Senate is made up of 51 Republicans and 49 Democrats -","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"so any testimony","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"she gives","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"on the allegations","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"could prove pivotal .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"Some have said","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"there should not be a vote on his confirmation","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"until Prof Ford has been heard .","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"President Trump weighed in heavily on the allegations on social media on Friday .","depth":5},{"id":88,"text":"In a series of tweets , he questioned","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"why law enforcement was not called at the time of the alleged assault , in 1982 .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"He also reiterated his full support for Judge Kavanaugh","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"who he described as a `` fine man , with an impeccable reputation '' .","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"Mr Trump 's controversial comments were criticised by Democratic politicians and some Republicans .","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"Republican Senator Susan Collins said","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"she was `` appalled '' by Mr Trump 's tweet .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"`` We know","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"that allegations of sexual assault","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"- I 'm not saying","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"that 's what happened in this case -","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"but we know","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"that allegations of sexual assault","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"are one of the most unreported crimes","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"that exist , ''","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"she told reporters .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"Only 23 % of rapes and sexual assaults are reported to the police ,","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"according to the Department of Justice 's 2016 report .","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"On Friday , the hashtag # WhyIDidntReport trended on Twitter ,","depth":5},{"id":107,"text":"with thousands sharing personal stories of sexual harassment and assault .","depth":5},{"id":108,"text":"Patti Davis , the daughter of President Ronald Reagan , wrote in the Washington Post","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"that she was raped 40 years ago .","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"`` It does n't surprise me","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"that for more than 30 years , Christine Blasey Ford did n't talk about the assault","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"she remembers , ''","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"she wrote ,","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"adding :","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"`` It 's important to understand how memory works in a traumatic event . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":231,"left":185,"right":230,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":158,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":139,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":133,"right":138,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":133,"left":120,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":118,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":117,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":117,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":132,"left":124,"right":131,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":123,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":5,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":6,"right":121,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":131,"left":126,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":125,"right":12,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":13,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":14,"right":128,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":128,"left":127,"right":17,"relation":"condi